Usage: createPtnFeedthrough [-help] <feedBox> [<layerId>] [-name <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<feedBox>          # Specifies the lower left x ,lower left y, upper right x
                   # and upper right y coordinates of the feedthrough area
                   # (box, required)
<layerId>          # Specifies the metal layer where pins are not to be
                   # created. (int, optional)
-name <string>     # Specifies the name of the routing feedthrough.
                   # (string, optional)